{"tid":2192838,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"黃之鋒遭四車跟蹤 花個半鐘甩身","createTime":"2020-09-07T11:23:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-07T13:29:57.000Z","uid":25558,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"55d24a76c2d4a8ddc78371d0416b5cd823d21c8e","tid":2192838,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T11:23:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200907/MCVPI5X76VCJHGL6MH5SKZW6ZU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200907%2FMCVPI5X76VCJHGL6MH5SKZW6ZU%2F&d=YmBpLFXYotmGfWLbQLkNpy8lxPyN12Ak3mY6G5vlvHI%3D&h=9b0ff4ec\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200907%2FMCVPI5X76VCJHGL6MH5SKZW6ZU%2F&h=24fe7a16\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200907/MCVPI5X76VCJHGL6MH5SKZW6ZU/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n黃之鋒遭四車跟蹤 花個半鐘甩身<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/blhp0O6txFTd6w_7hzvg2nLvV_Q=/1771x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/VPZHY24Q6NGGPGMIR4CSTXLTJY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fblhp0O6txFTd6w_7hzvg2nLvV_Q%3D%2F1771x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FVPZHY24Q6NGGPGMIR4CSTXLTJY.jpg&h=7ab2ef71&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■黃之鋒昨現身街頭受訪，呼籲關注被內地扣留的12人。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n黃之鋒昨午在逸東酒店外接受訪問，當時已發現被人跟蹤。他說當時已感覺奇怪，「行出酒店之後，越跟蹤就越明顯，繼續喺條街度行真係搞唔掂」，於是他上車希望擺脫他們，「點知，上咗車之後，跟蹤嘅車隊可謂陣容鼎盛，至少一架黑色五人私家車，兩架Honda銀色七人車，仲有架電單車，實在相當誇張。」結果他花了個半鐘遊勻港島九龍才能撇甩車隊。他呼籲同路人「真係要步步為營，永遠唔知道佢哋國安部門，用呢啲咁純熟嘅跟蹤技巧，會唔會用嚟翌日拘捕任何一個人。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「對港人靈活抗爭有信心」<br />\n<br />\n黃昨日接受訪問時呼籲港人關注被中國海警拘捕並正扣留內地的李宇軒等12人，他又在facebook發文譴責政府剝奪港人公民權利。街頭運動被政權打壓，他說：「有人問現在是否重回後雨傘的局面？我的答案很簡單 &mdash;&mdash; 經過六年磨練，我對香港人靈活多變的抗爭模式有相當信心。」<br />\n<br />\n由記者轉戰政壇的「立場姐姐」何桂藍昨日亦有現身抗爭現場，下午約4時，防暴警察在豉油街與西洋菜南街交界截查包括何桂藍的十多名途人，核對各人身份證及搜查隨身物品，何桂藍最終獲放行。<br />\n<br />\n藝人阮民安（Tommy）則手持彩虹色雨傘前往油麻地，他說，原本昨天是立法會選舉日，但被取消，惟有趁假日行街，「見好多兄弟姊妹今日出嚟，而我身為MK Pop始祖，唔好漏低我，我喺旺角出現好正常。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/7F3Dbl93cW7ukAGOF2cR4EfnZo4=/1329x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/CRKWRYFDBRATHO7YXCNMI7HHRM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F7F3Dbl93cW7ukAGOF2cR4EfnZo4%3D%2F1329x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FCRKWRYFDBRATHO7YXCNMI7HHRM.jpg&h=3cd55195&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■何桂藍（右）昨在旺角被防暴帶入封鎖線截查，後獲放行。"},{"pid":"61773323abab07884e86c86999df1628f318b723","tid":2192838,"uid":164965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T11:28:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8e887c319eaa2646adb256c4aaea687c8f938d7","tid":2192838,"uid":59328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T11:28:32.000Z","msg":"入隧道啦"},{"pid":"e5b604acc98fbcb282701eb7bbe72e03b0ff3146","tid":2192838,"uid":236414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T11:28:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6354ed6668eb3958cc17c5be287ef4cd53be7581","tid":2192838,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T11:28:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"856147d3b1c8895c79755ba3ff70e3d359182339","tid":2192838,"uid":165749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"55d24a76c2d4a8ddc78371d0416b5cd823d21c8e","tid":2192838,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T11:23:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/2020